在AIFriends目录下上传后端代码：`scp -r backend 服务器名:`

## 2.3 部署项目

### 2.3.1 安装部署工具

安装`nginx`:

```shell
sudo apt update
sudo apt install nginx
```

安装`gunicorn`：`pip3.14 install gunicorn --upgrade --user`

  ### 2.3.2 配置django项目

修改`backend/settings.py`文件：

- `DEBUG = False`

收集静态文件：

`python3.14 manage.py collectstatic`

### 2.3.3  配置 Gunicorn (应用服务)

运行`gunicorn`，在`/home/lh/backend/`目录下执行：

`gunicorn --workers 3 --graceful-timeout 3 --bind unix:/home/acs/backend/gunicorn.sock backend.wsgi:application`

### 2.3.4 配置 Nginx (反向代理)

将https证书复制到自己的服务器上，每年11月份左右要手动更新

```shell
/etc/nginx/cert/acapp.key
/etc/nginx/cert/acapp.pem
```

在/etc/nginx/mime.types中添加mjs类型

```shell
将 application/javascript      js;
改为 application/javascript      js mjs;
```

配置`/etc/nginx/nginx.conf`(关键是改域名):

```nginx
user lh;
worker_processes auto;
pid /run/nginx.pid;
error_log /var/log/nginx/error.log;
include /etc/nginx/modules-enabled/*.conf;

events {
    worker_connections 768;
}

http {
    sendfile on;
    tcp_nopush on;
    tcp_nodelay on;
    keepalive_timeout 65;
    types_hash_max_size 2048;

    include /etc/nginx/mime.types;
    default_type application/octet-stream;

    ssl_protocols TLSv1.2 TLSv1.3; # 删除了不安全的 TLSv1.0 和 1.1
    ssl_prefer_server_ciphers on;

    access_log /var/log/nginx/access.log;

    gzip on;
    gzip_disable "msie6";

    server {
        listen 80;
        server_name aifriends.store;
        return 301 https://$host$request_uri;
    }

    server {
        listen 443 ssl;
        server_name aifriends.store;

        ssl_certificate     /etc/nginx/cert/acapp.pem;
        ssl_certificate_key /etc/nginx/cert/acapp.key;

        ssl_session_timeout 5m;
        ssl_ciphers ECDHE-RSA-AES128-GCM-SHA256:HIGH:!aNULL:!MD5:!RC4:!DHE;

        location /static/ {
            alias /home/lh/backend/static/;
            expires 30d;
        }

        location /media/ {
            alias /home/lh/backend/media/;
            expires 30d;
        }

        location / {
            proxy_set_header Host $host;
            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;

 proxy_pass http://unix:/home/lh/backend/gunicorn.sock;
        }
    }

    include /etc/nginx/conf.d/*.conf;
    include /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/*;
}

```

加载nginx配置：`sudo nginx -s reload`

# 3.数据迁移

## 3.1 安装mysql的客户端与服务端
~~~shell
```
# 更新软件源（确保能找到最新包）
sudo apt update

# 安装 MySQL 服务端 + 客户端完整包（一次性装全）
sudo apt install -y mysql-server mysql-client
```
~~~

## 3.2 设置 MySQL 开机自启（避免重启服务器后服务停止）

```shell
sudo systemctl enable mysql
```

## 3.3 修改Mysql的root用户密码

```sql
sudo mysql -u root
-- 切换到 mysql 系统库
USE mysql;

# 2. 给root用户授权「从任意IP+新密码」登录（覆盖所有权限问题）
ALTER USER 'root'@'%' IDENTIFIED WITH mysql_native_password BY '你的新密码';
-- 本地登录
ALTER USER 'root'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED WITH mysql_native_password BY '你的新密码';
-- 制刷新权限
FLUSH PRIVILEGES;  


-- 退出 MySQL
EXIT;
```

